<br>
I have a feeling it was caused by lag and that either buff information and/or equipment information is stored client side so if the server finishes zoninging you but your computer lags before it could tell the server what buffs/equipment you had the server counts you as dead since it knows enough damage was dont to kill you @ base hit points.<br>
<br>
Not really expecting them to change it anytime soon (been that way for what, almost 2 years now?) so just adjust to the pluses and minuses.<br>
